Have you heard? Several space-time rifts have appeared near the Academy! 
And to make matters worse, giant demons have been spotted coming out of the rifts!

It will take more than one or two individuals to eliminate this threat.
Join forces with other alchemists to defeat the demons!
You can enter the time rifts to counter the invading demons via the "Demon Invasion" icon in the bottom left corner of the map.
The more damage dealt to the demons, the more rewards you will get!

Every demon has a weakness. 
Identify and exploit their weaknesses to gain the upper hand in battle.
